<H4>

<s docid="FBIS4-44904" num="10"> Large Satellites for Future Launch</s>
</H4>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS4-44904" num="11"> 94FE0426F Tokyo NIKKAN KOGYO SHIMBUN in Japanese 5 Feb 94 p 18--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY</s>
</F>
