<s docid="FBIS3-23691" num="8"> Russia's Space Plans to End of Decade</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-23691" num="9"> 947Q0088 Moscow ZEMLYA I VSELENNAYA in Russian No 5, Sep-Oct 93 pp 3-11</s>
