<s docid="LA021290-0037" num="8"> PROSPECTS OF TRAVERSING THE HEAVENS LEAVE THE NATION MOONSTRUCK OVER THE SCIENTIFIC -- AND COMMERCIAL -- POSSIBILITIES.</s>
